<li>In addition to Cys-32 and Cys-34 , there are three other cysteine residues in the ArsR protein : Cys-37 , Cys-108 , and Cys-116 .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=8621591" target="_blank">8621591</a>]<br></li></div>
